"#6a6a6a","subheading_font_size":12,"subheading_font_size_m":11,"subheading_spacing_bottom":8,"title":"Our Mission & Vision","caption":"The BEDGEAR Foundation's mission is to inspire the best in every individual around the globe through the innovation and introduction of a personalized, modular Performance sleep system, while addressing the environmental issues facing our planet and building world peace through commerce.\n\n<br>\n<br>\nLegal Status – Nonprofit designation, EIN, etc.","color":"#ffffff","padding_top":50,"padding_bottom":30,"padding_top_m":36,"padding_bottom_m":36}},"block_icons_7tMrai":{"type":"block-icons","blocks":{"icon_block_EW8Tw9":{"type":"icon_block","settings":{"icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/community_outreach_icon_798bb642-572f-4003-95ef-d61233a96395.svg","title":"Community Outreach","text":""}},"icon_block_n6mzkh":{"type":"icon_block","settings":{"icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/donations_icon_e396bc94-5acd-44c7-95b1-fca1f94531a7.svg","title":"Donations & Partners","text":""}},"icon_block_iyd3jc":{"type":"icon_block","settings":{"icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/education_icon_e7ffe3a1-96f1-433b-8c10-6f91d7b5c426.svg","title":"Education","text":""}},"icon_block_YJVGqh":{"type":"icon_block","settings":{"icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/disaster_relief_icon_57c414b7-afcf-461b-933d-6616beafcd1d.svg","title":"Disaster Relief","text":""}}},"block_order":["icon_block_EW8Tw9","icon_block_n6mzkh","icon_block_iyd3jc","icon_block_YJVGqh"],"name":"Block Icons","settings":{"padding_top_desktop":20,"padding_bottom_desktop":60,"padding_top_mobile":40,"padding_bottom_mobile":40,"eyebrow":"","heading":"Programs & Initiatives","subheading":"","content_alignment":"center","max_width":1520,"title_line_height":0.6,"icon_wrapper_size":72,"icon_size":40,"header_spacing":40,"eyebrow_font_size_desktop":12,"heading_font_size_desktop":34,"eyebrow_font_size_mobile":14,"heading_font_size_mobile":26}},"card_grid_EVf7Kb":{"type":"card-grid","blocks":{"card_eKXpPe":{"type":"card","settings":{"heading":"Recovery For Hurrican Victims","description":"<p>When Hurricane Harvey left thousands of families displaced, the BEDGEAR Foundation pledged to support the recovery efforts for its victims. The BEDGEAR Foundation donated all online proceeds for a day to the Dirk Nowitzki Foundation, which benefited families and children affected by the hurricane. Additionally, a donation of pillows and blankets went to the relief efforts of the Dallas Mavericks and the Houston Furniture Bank. In total, nearly half a million dollars in product and monetary donations were donated, and matched by Mark Cuban, to support home rebuilding.<\/p>","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/hurrican_victims_aid.jpg","image_aspect":"21 \/ 9"}},"card_APzYGK":{"type":"card","settings":{"heading":"Wild Fire Aid","description":"<p>In response to wildfires that devastated Sonoma, Napa, and Solano counties in Northern California, the BEDGEAR Foundation donated hundreds of pillows, blankets, and sheets to support the outreach efforts of Sleep City Beds. Their Windsor store manager, Mark Luce, lost his home in the fires, and seven employees were also forced to evacuate. Sleep City Beds teams coordinated local distribution, personally delivering BEDGEAR products and donated mattresses to evacuees and firefighters who traveled from out of town to battle the fires.<\/p>","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/wild_fire_aid.jpg","image_aspect":"21 \/ 9"}},"card_jdxJRz":{"type":"card","settings":{"heading":"Hope To Dream","description":"<p>The BEDGEAR Foundation is a proud partner of Ashley HomeStore’s Hope to Dream program, which helps deliver the gift of sleep to children in need. The program ensures that every child has a clean, unused mattress of their own by donating a portion of proceeds from mattress sales at participating locations. Through this partnership, children receive a complete sleep setup including a mattress, bed frame, sheets, blankets, and pillows. Since 2010, the BEDGEAR Foundation has donated hundreds of pillows, sheet sets, and mattress protectors to support children’s sleep needs.<\/p>","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/hope_to_dream.jpg","image_aspect":"21 \/ 9"}},"card_FHFjrq":{"type":"card","settings":{"heading":"Giving Back With Impact Day","description":"<p>Every year, the BEDGEAR Foundation hosts IMPACT Day, bringing together teams from the New York and Rock Hill offices to partner with a local charity and give back to the community. Last year, in partnership with Pilgrims’ Inn, the Foundation assembled hundreds of care packages for homeless women and children living in the shelter. As a business rooted in York County, giving back is central to the BEDGEAR Foundation’s mission. The care packages included essential household items, coats, kids’ pillows, and school supplies, and the team looks forward to continuing this tradition this holiday season.<\/p><p><\/p>","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/asset_5.jpg","image_aspect":"21 \/ 9"}}},"block_order":["card_eKXpPe","card_APzYGK","card_jdxJRz","card_FHFjrq"],"name":"Card Grid (Manual Blocks)","settings":{"section_heading":"Global Support","section_description":"<p>From hurricane recovery to wildfire relief, we bring the gift of sleep where it’s needed most.<\/p>","header_alignment":"center","section_heading_size":34,"section_description_size":16,"columns_desktop":2,"heading_size":24,"description_size":14,"background_color":"#f4f4f4","card_background_color":"#ffffff","max_width":1520,"padding_y":48,"padding_x":24,"gap":28,"card_radius":22,"image_radius":14,"card_shadow":"0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)"}},"searvice_team_pNfbWB":{"type":"searvice-team","blocks":{"support_card_LPCBbj":{"type":"support_card","settings":{"title":"fbvfvsdv","description":"dvdsvdvds","button_text":"vdvdsvdvdsvds","button_url":""}},"support_card_4gFTQ7":{"type":"support_card","settings":{"title":"vdvdvdsdsvds","description":"vdsvdsvdvvdvd","button_text":"","button_url":""}},"support_card_ABXtDB":{"ty